description._content: Catalog #: 09_01141 Title: Kathryn Fritz Special Collection Photo San Diego California Date: circa 1927 Additional Information: One man and one woman standing in front of Ryan M-1 mail plane aircraft, Kathryn Fritz was a young woman residing in San Diego during the 1920s.
